 Analyst review: "Odetics has grown into a major player in the data storage 
field. The bulk of its revenues are generated from its ATL Products division, 
which manufactures automated tape library systems. The company's technology is 
quite impressive, providing applications for industries ranging from television 
broadcasting stations like PBS to computer makers like E-Systems and Cray 
