<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Ventura numbers -- A story Sunday on U2 of "On the Rebound," a special guide 
to help those affected by the earthquake, may have been misleading in the way 
it listed telephone numbers for city building inspection departments. Those 
needing to call their local inspection office can find a full list of Ventura 
County cities and their individual inspection department numbers on U7 of that 
section. 
</P>
